WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:05.147
Now to that ABC News exclusive and that extraordinary footage inside the plane crash.

00:06.473 --> 00:10.353
This, we wanna show you, is the kind of camera it was shot on.

00:10.457 --> 00:14.446
It's called a GoPro camera, and it's a remarkable, remarkable video.

00:14.735 --> 00:15.212
Take a look.

00:20.708 --> 00:22.324
Those passengers don't know it yet,...

00:22.427 --> 00:27.073
...but they are seconds away from experiencing the worst fear of every air traveler.

00:29.493 --> 00:31.207
Suddenly, the alarm sounds.

00:33.364 --> 00:36.785
The plane is going down, spiraling into the ocean.

00:56.987 --> 01:01.117
A mad scramble as water fills the inside of the plane.

01:08.926 --> 01:10.835
Survivors going for the exits,...

01:23.775 --> 01:26.512
...clinging to anything they can get their hands on.

